                     <interp inst="t17870523-39-person474" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            , of Sharp's-alley,</p>
               <p>"Cow-cross, bricklayer, maketh oath,</p>
               <p>"that he went with Daniel Smith, to</p>
               <p>"the assistance of 
